Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.52,0:01:33.61,Main01,Somebody,0000,0000,0000,,Moving targets will appear between your hands, and a balance line will be drawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.61,0:01:35.06,Main01,Reborn,0000,0000,0000,,Ciao-su.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.06,0:01:38.17,Main01,Reborn,0000,0000,0000,,Gokudera and the others were headed for the enemy base,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.17,0:01:41.11,Main01,Reborn,0000,0000,0000,,but Shoichi Irie started up the mobile block,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.11,0:01:43.08,Main01,Reborn,0000,0000,0000,,so everyone was separated.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.21,0:01:57.91,Main01,Reborn,0000,0000,0000,,Gokudera completed SISTEMA C.A.I. as he fought Lightning Gamma to a draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.02,0:02:02.11,Main01,Yamamoto,0000,0000,0000,,Shigure Soen Ryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.11,0:02:03.86,Main01,Yamamoto,0000,0000,0000,,Stance 10:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.83,0:02:07.19,Main01,Yamamoto,0000,0000,0000,,Scontro di Rondine!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.88,0:02:18.99,Main01,Yamamoto,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-at...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.99,0:02:23.99,Main01,Reborn,0000,0000,0000,,Yamamoto put up a fight against the greatest swordsman, the Phantom Knight,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.99,0:02:26.27,Main01,Reborn,0000,0000,0000,,but he was one step short and was defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.63,0:02:28.08,Main01,Reborn,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.08,0:02:30.84,Main01,SoldierB,0000,0000,0000,,That's Mukuro Rokudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.09,0:02:33.30,Main01,Chrome,0000,0000,0000,,Negative.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.30,0:02:34.95,Main01,Chrome,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Chrome.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.95,0:02:36.48,Main01,SoldierC,0000,0000,0000,,What? A woman?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.48,0:02:38.10,Main01,SoldierB,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Vongola! Open fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.69,0:02:47.85,Main01,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,There's more than one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.85,0:02:50.27,Main01,Lambo,0000,0000,0000,,Boo! Nosebleed boom!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.27,0:02:52.30,Main01,I-Pin,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was gonna suffocate in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.50,0:02:58.73,Main01,Reborn,0000,0000,0000,,And Tsuna now seeks to perfect the X BURNER with Spanner's help.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.18,0:03:00.08,Main01,Tsuna,0000,0000,0000,,Reborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.08,0:03:02.54,Main01,Reborn,0000,0000,0000,,The dots are finally starting to connect.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.04,0:03:08.07,Main01,Reborn,0000,0000,0000,,That device must have something to do with why we can't return to the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.50,0:03:12.78,Main01,Tsuna,0000,0000,0000,,So this infiltration plan wasn't a mistake...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.78,0:03:16.75,Main01,Tsuna,0000,0000,0000,,Now we know why we have to defeat Irie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.86,0:03:24.26,Main01,Reborn,0000,0000,0000,,We'll capture Shoichi Irie and force him to tell us how to return to the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.50,0:03:32.53,Main01,Bird,0000,0000,0000,,Hibari! Hibari!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.78,0:03:37.36,Main01,Phantom,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.91,0:03:40.07,Main01,Phantom,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoya Hibari from ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.29,0:03:45.46,Main01,Phantom,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.23,0:03:52.32,Main01,Phantom,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoya Hibari possesses mist waves allowing him the use of the Mist Ring,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.32,0:03:54.81,Main01,Phantom,0000,0000,0000,,but he shouldn't be able to conjure such an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.20,0:04:00.60,Main01,Phantom,0000,0000,0000,,Falling for an illusion means losing control of your perceptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.60,0:04:04.08,Main01,Phantom,0000,0000,0000,,I would never be fooled by such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.09,0:04:06.76,Main01,Phantom,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.76,0:04:10.23,Main01,Phantom,0000,0000,0000,,He's the real Kyoya Hibari from ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.58,0:04:14.60,Main01,Phantom,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the time travel I've heard so much about...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.10,0:04:16.91,Main01,Hibari,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of trick is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.38,0:04:21.14,Main01,Hibari,0000,0000,0000,,I believe I was just taking a nap on my school's roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.83,0:04:23.10,Main01,Hibari,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, pal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:26.82,Main01,Hibari,0000,0000,0000,,In Nami Middle,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.16,0:04:29.31,Main01,Hibari,0000,0000,0000,,those eyebrows would violate school regulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.38,0:04:33.21,Main01,Phantom,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.21,0:04:34.70,Main01,Hibari,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.70,0:04:36.23,Main01,Hibari,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.58,0:04:41.55,Main01,Hibari,0000,0000,0000,,Why is our school's missing student lying unconscious here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.20,0:04:45.79,Main01,Phantom,0000,0000,0000,,I defeated Takeshi Yamamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.82,0:04:48.10,Main01,Hibari,0000,0000,0000,,You did?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.10,0:04:49.74,Main01,Hibari,0000,0000,0000,,That simplifies things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.70,0:04:54.65,Main01,Hibari,0000,0000,0000,,Your actions can be considered an attack on Nami Middle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.65,0:04:57.03,Main01,Hibari,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, I will dole out the appropriate punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.66,0:05:01.85,Main01,Phantom,0000,0000,0000,,This man knows nothing of this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.88,0:05:06.22,Main01,Phantom,0000,0000,0000,,Am I overanalyzing the situation by assuming that Kyoya Hibari...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.22,0:05:11.33,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,knowingly brought this past version of himself here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.33,0:05:12.87,Main01,Phantom,0000,0000,0000,,But this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.21,0:05:16.48,Main01,Phantom,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.48,0:05:17.79,Main01,Hibari,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.32,0:05:30.89,Main01,Phantom,0000,0000,0000,,You may be Kyoya Hibari, but a mere child is no match for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.67,0:05:42.56,Main01,Tsuna,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.12,0:05:49.14,Main01,Tsuna,0000,0000,0000,,X STREAM!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.32,0:06:00.61,Main01,Iris,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing, scum?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.61,0:06:03.16,Main01,Iris,0000,0000,0000,,This is all you're capable of!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.16,0:06:05.66,Main01,Iris,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need useless trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.73,0:06:11.24,Main01,Reborn,0000,0000,0000,,Keep at it, Tsuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.24,0:06:13.22,Main01,Reborn,0000,0000,0000,,The item will be completed soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.74,0:06:17.48,Main01,Reborn,0000,0000,0000,,A perfect X BURNER should be able to...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.48,0:06:19.45,Main01,Ginger,0000,0000,0000,,Foolish fools...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.04,0:06:29.80,Main01,Iris,0000,0000,0000,,You sure took your time getting here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.80,0:06:30.96,Main01,Iris,0000,0000,0000,,Ginger Bread!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.96,0:06:32.11,Main01,Ginger,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.35,0:06:44.12,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Cíl 129\NOperace X
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.83,0:06:54.63,Main01,Phantom,0000,0000,0000,,Musím přiznat, jsem ohromený.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.63,0:06:56.04,Main01,Hibari,0000,0000,0000,,O čem to mluvíš?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.04,0:07:00.39,Main01,Hibari,0000,0000,0000,,Zvykl sis na rychlost mých mečů během krátké chvíle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.39,0:07:01.10,Main01,Phantom,0000,0000,0000,,Nicméně!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.99,0:07:12.66,Main01,Phantom,0000,0000,0000,,Jsi jenom dítě.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.54,0:07:19.11,Main01,Hibari,0000,0000,0000,,Nemám rád, když mi tak říkají.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.30,0:07:28.82,Main01,Reborn,0000,0000,0000,,Kdo je to?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.82,0:07:31.83,Main01,Spanner,0000,0000,0000,,Vice Kapitán 8. Jednotky, Ginger Bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.34,0:07:34.79,Main01,Spanner,0000,0000,0000,,Také známý jako "Kouzelnická Loutka".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.19,0:07:37.25,Main01,Spanner,0000,0000,0000,,Buď opatrný, Vongolo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.25,0:07:40.23,Main01,Spanner,0000,0000,0000,,To není skutečné tělo Ginger Breada. Je to jenom loutka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.23,0:07:41.91,Main01,Tsuna,0000,0000,0000,,Loutka...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.91,0:07:42.98,Main01,Tsuna,0000,0000,0000,,Zase, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.98,0:07:45.26,Main01,Yamamoto,0000,0000,0000,,Jsi úžasná, Lal Mirchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.68,0:07:48.16,Main01,Ryohei,0000,0000,0000,,Vedla sis extrémně dobře, když to porazilas.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.16,0:07:50.79,Main01,Ryohei,0000,0000,0000,,Jsi o krok blíž k pomstění našeho mistra.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.84,0:07:53.34,Main01,Lal,0000,0000,0000,,Nevyhrála jsem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.33,0:07:55.58,Main01,Lal,0000,0000,0000,,Podívejte.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.14,0:07:59.23,Main01,Ryohei,0000,0000,0000,,Co...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.23,0:08:00.25,Main01,Ryohei,0000,0000,0000,,L-loutka?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.25,0:08:03.92,Main01,Lal,0000,0000,0000,,To je důvod, proč se Gingerovi říká "Kouzelnická Loutka".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.66,0:08:08.12,Main01,Lal,0000,0000,0000,,Nikdo nikdy nebyl schopný ho dorazit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.12,0:08:09.81,Main01,Reborn,0000,0000,0000,,Chápu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.81,0:08:12.93,Main01,Reborn,0000,0000,0000,,Takže proto se mu říká Kouzelnická loutka.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.93,0:08:16.68,Main01,Spanner,0000,0000,0000,,Nikdo neví, kde je jeho skutečné tělo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.38,0:08:19.29,Main01,Ginger,0000,0000,0000,,Dokone ani zrádce, jako ty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.67,0:08:24.23,Main01,Spanner,0000,0000,0000,,Tvoje super intuice nebude fungovat na loutku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.91,0:08:28.62,Main01,Ginger,0000,0000,0000,,Spannere, tys nás opravdu zradil.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.62,0:08:30.61,Main01,Ginger,0000,0000,0000,,Nechci mít nic společného se zrádci!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.01,0:08:31.98,Main01,Tsuna,0000,0000,0000,,Uhni, Spannere!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.88,0:08:37.65,Main01,Tsuna,0000,0000,0000,,S-Spannere...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.61,0:08:43.34,Main01,Iris,0000,0000,0000,,Dostali jsme ho.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.87,0:08:47.40,Main01,Tsuna,0000,0000,0000,,Spannere...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.92,0:08:54.54,Main01,Spanner,0000,0000,0000,,Nepodceňujte duši mechanika!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.54,0:08:56.61,Main01,Spanner,0000,0000,0000,,Řekl jsem, že tu práci dokončím,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.61,0:08:58.52,Main01,Spanner,0000,0000,0000,,tak ji taky dokončím!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.52,0:09:01.46,Main01,Iris,0000,0000,0000,,Snaží se vyrobit něco divného!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.46,0:09:03.94,Main01,Iris,0000,0000,0000,,Dostaň ho jako prvního, Gingere!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.41,0:09:05.91,Main01,Ginger,0000,0000,0000,,Souhlas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.91,0:09:07.57,Main01,Tsuna,0000,0000,0000,,To není dobré...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.10,0:09:11.55,Main01,Iris,0000,0000,0000,,No tak, no tak!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.63,0:09:16.03,Main01,Spanner,0000,0000,0000,,Už jen chviličku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.41,0:09:17.72,Main01,Tsuna,0000,0000,0000,,Spannere!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.72,0:09:20.45,Main01,Ginger,0000,0000,0000,,Zrádce! Zrádce!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.45,0:09:22.52,Main01,Ginger,0000,0000,0000,,Nechci mít nic společného se zrádci!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.95,0:09:24.36,Main01,Spanner,0000,0000,0000,,Už jen chviličku...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.36,0:09:26.25,Main01,Spanner,0000,0000,0000,,Jenom... chviličku...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.46,0:09:30.95,Main01,Ginger,0000,0000,0000,,Pá-pá, Spannere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.95,0:09:31.91,Main01,Tsuna,0000,0000,0000,,Sakra!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.24,0:09:34.14,Main01,Spanner,0000,0000,0000,,Hotovo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.14,0:09:35.59,Main01,Reborn,0000,0000,0000,,Spannere, nad tebou!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.43,0:09:40.63,Main01,Tsuna,0000,0000,0000,,Spannere! Spannere!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.22,0:09:45.75,Main01,Iris,0000,0000,0000,,Tohle je osud každého zrádce!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.75,0:09:47.64,Main01,Iris,0000,0000,0000,,Dobrá práce!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.10,0:09:49.17,Main01,Tsuna,0000,0000,0000,,Spannere...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.17,0:09:50.10,Main01,Tsuna,0000,0000,0000,,Neříkej, že...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.94,0:10:11.06,Main01,Spanner,0000,0000,0000,,Vem si je, Vongolo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.01,0:10:17.61,Main01,Ginger,0000,0000,0000,,To se nestane!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.61,0:10:19.75,Main01,Iris,0000,0000,0000,,Chyťte toho Vongolského kluka!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.74,0:10:28.51,Main01,Iris,0000,0000,0000,,Dostali jsme ho?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.15,0:10:50.93,Main01,Tsuna,0000,0000,0000,,Je ještě moc brzy na to jít spát, Spannere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.15,0:10:58.40,Main01,Tsuna,0000,0000,0000,,Chci se ujistit, že uvidíš...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.97,0:11:05.37,Main01,Tsuna,0000,0000,0000,,dokonalý X-BURNER, který chtěls vidět!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.67,0:11:21.45,Main01,Tsuna,0000,0000,0000,,Je ještě moc brzy na to jít spát, Spannere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.60,0:11:29.07,Main01,Tsuna,0000,0000,0000,,Chci se ujistit, že uvidíš...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.95,0:11:34.37,Main01,Tsuna,0000,0000,0000,,dokonalý X-BURNER, který chtěls vidět!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.82,0:11:36.13,Main01,Ginger,0000,0000,0000,,X-BURNER?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.80,0:11:39.21,Main01,Giannini,0000,0000,0000,,Čočky!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.21,0:11:41.26,Main01,Giannini,0000,0000,0000,,Nasadil si ty čočky?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.26,0:11:42.27,Main01,Reborn,0000,0000,0000,,Žádný strach.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.27,0:11:44.14,Main01,Reborn,0000,0000,0000,,Jsou v pořádku.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.46,0:11:47.76,Main01,Iris,0000,0000,0000,,Cože?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.76,0:11:50.01,Main01,Iris,0000,0000,0000,,Co se snaží udělat?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.82,0:11:55.26,Main01,Reborn,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuno, víš jak je používat, že?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.79,0:11:56.82,Main01,Tsuna,0000,0000,0000,,Ano.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.10,0:12:00.43,Main01,Ginger,0000,0000,0000,,Předvádíš nám tu úžasnou show,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.43,0:12:02.32,Main01,Ginger,0000,0000,0000,,ale vsadím se, že jenom blafuješ.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.51,0:12:09.25,Main01,Spanner,0000,0000,0000,,Dovol mi ti to vysvětlit, Vongolo...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.72,0:12:14.94,Main01,Spanner,0000,0000,0000,,Ze všeho nejdřív, ty čočky jsou propojené s tvými sluchátky.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.94,0:12:17.87,Main01,Spanner,0000,0000,0000,,Měl bys z nich slyšet veškeré informace.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.87,0:12:19.38,Main01,Tsuna,0000,0000,0000,,Slyšet?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.38,0:12:20.36,Main01,Spanner,0000,0000,0000,,Ano.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.36,0:12:22.36,Main01,Spanner,0000,0000,0000,,Další věcí je zobrazovací display.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.36,0:12:25.25,Main01,Spanner,0000,0000,0000,,Horní ručička je pro pravou rukavici,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.25,0:12:29.50,Main01,Spanner,0000,0000,0000,,a dolní ručička zobrazuje levou rukavici.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.50,0:12:31.38,Main01,Spanner,0000,0000,0000,,Tvrdý Plamen bude mít červenou stupnici.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.38,0:12:34.89,Main01,Spanner,0000,0000,0000,,Jemný Plamen bude zobrazovat zelená stupnice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.71,0:12:39.50,Main01,Tsuna,0000,0000,0000,,Tak fajn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.50,0:12:41.09,Main01,Tsuna,0000,0000,0000,,Funguje to tak jak má.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.75,0:12:44.04,Main01,Spanner,0000,0000,0000,,Pro X-Burner použij...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.04,0:12:50.66,Main01,Spanner,0000,0000,0000,,slova "Operace X". Ty automaticky aktivují zaměřovací systém.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.66,0:12:53.30,Main01,Tsuna,0000,0000,0000,,Operation X?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.30,0:12:55.13,Main01,Spanner,0000,0000,0000,,Ano. Nezapomeň na to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.13,0:12:58.49,Main01,Reborn,0000,0000,0000,,Nebylo by to vtipné, kdybys to udělal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.49,0:13:00.38,Main01,Tsuna,0000,0000,0000,,Ano, rozumím.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.38,0:13:02.86,Main01,Spanner,0000,0000,0000,,Jakmile jednou řekneš "Operace X,"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.86,0:13:05.56,Main01,Spanner,0000,0000,0000,,display se přepne do X-BURNER modu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.56,0:13:11.77,Main01,Spanner,0000,0000,0000,,Uvede se tak do pohybu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.77,0:13:14.47,Main01,Spanner,0000,0000,0000,,Abys mohl vystřelit stabilní X-BURNER,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.47,0:13:16.91,Main01,Spanner,0000,0000,0000,,musí být cíl uprostřed,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.71,0:13:19.01,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4}Ukazatel rovnováhy
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.71,0:13:19.01,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6}Cíl
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.91,0:13:20.26,Main01,Spanner,0000,0000,0000,,a výstupní Plamen musí být na obou stranách stejný.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.26,0:13:24.74,Main01,Spanner,0000,0000,0000,,To znamená, že tyhle dvě linky musí být vyrovnané.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.64,0:13:29.87,Main01,Ginger,0000,0000,0000,,To je k ničemu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.21,0:13:40.24,Main01,Tsuna,0000,0000,0000,,Operace...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.62,0:13:41.53,Main01,Tsuna,0000,0000,0000,,X.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.30,0:13:44.64,Main01,Contact,0000,0000,0000,,Rozumím, bossi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.64,0:13:48.55,Main01,Contact,0000,0000,0000,,Zahajování palebné sekvence pro X-BURNER.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.22,0:13:53.17,Main01,Spanner,0000,0000,0000,,Bude střílet hned na první pokus ze vzduchu...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.70,0:14:02.83,Main01,Iris,0000,0000,0000,,Plameny?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.83,0:14:04.44,Main01,Iris,0000,0000,0000,,Míří do opačného směru?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.59,0:14:09.08,Main01,Giannini,0000,0000,0000,,T-to je... úžasné!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.08,0:14:10.60,Main01,Giannini,0000,0000,0000,,To je úžasné!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.60,0:14:11.63,Main01,Reborn,0000,0000,0000,,Samozřejmě.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.75,0:14:13.94,Main01,StaffA,0000,0000,0000,,Ginger. Iris.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.94,0:14:15.14,Main01,StaffA,0000,0000,0000,,Slyšíte mě?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.99,0:14:19.93,Main01,StaffA,0000,0000,0000,,Rozluštili jsme záznam boje z Strau Moscova bojového záznamníku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.41,0:14:23.23,Main01,StaffA,0000,0000,0000,,Věříme, že Vongolův útok je technika, která uvolňuje...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.23,0:14:26.58,Main01,StaffA,0000,0000,0000,,obrovské množství energie tím směrem, kterým míří.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.58,0:14:28.82,Main01,Irie,0000,0000,0000,,Je to nebezpečné tam zůstat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.82,0:14:29.70,Main01,Irie,0000,0000,0000,,Rychle!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.70,0:14:30.56,Main01,Irie,0000,0000,0000,,Rychle, zmizte odtamtud!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.15,0:14:42.24,Main01,Gokudera,0000,0000,0000,,Sakra...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.58,0:14:47.03,Main01,Gokudera,0000,0000,0000,,J-já.. nemůžu se pohnout...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.23,0:14:50.27,Main01,Gokudera,0000,0000,0000,,Ale můžu říct...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.27,0:14:54.29,Main01,Gokudera,0000,0000,0000,,Ž-že náš Boss právě teď bojuje.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.29,0:14:58.77,Main01,Gokudera,0000,0000,0000,,a jeho pravá ruka tady jenom leží...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.41,0:15:01.14,Main01,Gokudera,0000,0000,0000,,Zapomeň na to, že pohneš rukou...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.14,0:15:03.70,Main01,Gokudera,0000,0000,0000,,Nemůžu pohnout ani prstem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.00,0:15:07.44,Main01,Gokudera,0000,0000,0000,,B-být takhle zbytečný ve chvíli jako je tato...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.30,0:15:10.04,Main01,Gokudera,0000,0000,0000,,S-sakra...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.40,0:15:30.97,Main01,Phantom,0000,0000,0000,,To je konec.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.64,0:15:44.29,Main01,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Chrome-san, nepřepínejte se tolik.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.29,0:15:45.13,Main01,Chrome,0000,0000,0000,,Jsem v pořádku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.89,0:15:47.75,Main01,Lambo,0000,0000,0000,,Kusamochi, udělejme si přestávku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.89,0:15:54.02,On Screen,Lambo,0000,0000,0000,,[Poznámka: "Kusamochi" (doslovně znamená tráva mochi).]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.75,0:15:49.64,Main01,Ipin,0000,0000,0000,,Lambo, buď vážný ve hledání!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.64,0:15:50.85,Main01,Ipin,0000,0000,0000,,Žádné přestávky nejsou povoleny!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.85,0:15:54.02,Main01,Lambo,0000,0000,0000,,Cože?! Ale Lambo-san má hlad!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.02,0:15:55.04,Main01,Lambo,0000,0000,0000,,A je unavený!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.76,0:15:57.00,Main01,Lambo,0000,0000,0000,,Au...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.00,0:15:58.63,Main01,Lambo,0000,0000,0000,,Vytáhněte mě.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.63,0:16:00.85,Main01,Ipin,0000,0000,0000,,Děláš moc potíží, Lambo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.85,0:16:02.30,Main01,Ipin,0000,0000,0000,,Honem. Chyť mě za ruku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.30,0:16:04.79,Main01,Lambo,0000,0000,0000,,Ale já na ni nedosáhnu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.79,0:16:06.07,Main01,Chrome,0000,0000,0000,,To je...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.00,0:16:08.29,Main01,Chrome,0000,0000,0000,,To je ono.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.59,0:16:11.79,Main01,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Kopejte.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.96,0:16:17.07,Main01,Lambo,0000,0000,0000,,Tohle je všechno díky Lambo-sanovi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.52,0:16:19.10,Main01,Ipin,0000,0000,0000,,Pomoz nám, Lambo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.57,0:16:21.92,Main01,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,T-to je...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.16,0:16:23.62,Main01,Chrome,0000,0000,0000,,Kdo je to?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.62,0:16:24.90,Main01,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Sasagawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.40,0:16:27.87,Main01,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Gokudera je asi pořád někde tady pohřbený.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.87,0:16:29.14,Main01,Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Podívejte se po něm!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.14,0:16:30.06,Main01,Ipin,0000,0000,0000,,Rozumím!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.06,0:16:32.06,Main01,Lambo,0000,0000,0000,,Rozumím...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.93,0:16:39.14,Main01,Contact,0000,0000,0000,,Pravá rukavice, jemný plamen, stabilizovano na 150,000 FV.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.14,0:16:45.48,Main01,Contact,0000,0000,0000,,Levá rukavice, přepínání z jemného plamene na tvrdý, nabíjení krystalu v rukavici energií Plamene.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.48,0:16:46.69,Main01,Ginger,0000,0000,0000,,Iris?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.69,0:16:49.28,Main01,Iris,0000,0000,0000,,Je to hodně silná střela?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.28,0:16:51.32,Main01,Iris,0000,0000,0000,,Vtipné.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.32,0:16:53.48,Main01,Iris,0000,0000,0000,,Hora svalů!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.50,0:17:02.08,Main01,Reborn,0000,0000,0000,,Chce ustát plný zásah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.58,0:17:06.66,Main01,Iris,0000,0000,0000,,Dívej se!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.66,0:17:11.15,Main01,Iris,0000,0000,0000,,Ať udělá ten Vongolský kluk cokoliv, tahle hora svalů to vydrží!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.15,0:17:12.54,Main01,Iris,0000,0000,0000,,Vzdej to!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.89,0:17:17.42,Main01,Contact,0000,0000,0000,,Cíl zaměřen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.80,0:17:20.16,Main01,Contact,0000,0000,0000,,Teplota Plamene v pravé rukavici stoupá.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.37,0:17:24.09,Main01,Contact,0000,0000,0000,,180,000...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.54,0:17:28.11,Main01,Contact,0000,0000,0000,,190,000...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.93,0:17:33.04,Main01,Contact,0000,0000,0000,,200,000 FV.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.32,0:17:39.64,Main01,Contact,0000,0000,0000,,Teplota Plamene v levé rukavici stoupá.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.64,0:17:40.70,Main01,Contact,0000,0000,0000,,180,000...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.54,0:17:44.80,Main01,Giannini,0000,0000,0000,,To... To je...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.25,0:17:49.03,Main01,Contact,0000,0000,0000,,190,000...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.03,0:17:51.13,Main01,Contact,0000,0000,0000,,200,000 FV.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.11,0:17:53.89,Main01,Contact,0000,0000,0000,,Stoprocentní Rovnováha.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.89,0:17:55.38,Main01,Contact,0000,0000,0000,,Připraveno k výstřelu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.27,0:17:59.72,Main01,Iris,0000,0000,0000,,Neustupujte!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.77,0:18:02.18,Main01,Tsuna,0000,0000,0000,,X-BURNER.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.40,0:18:16.43,Main01,Spanner,0000,0000,0000,,Je to stabilní...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.01,0:18:22.16,Main01,StaffB,0000,0000,0000,,Kamera je zničena!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.74,0:18:24.40,Main01,StaffA,0000,0000,0000,,Máme problém, Irie-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.40,0:18:25.61,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,Jakový?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.37,0:18:33.12,Main01,StaffA,0000,0000,0000,,Oblast od čtvrtého doku až ke třetímu byla kompletně zničena.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.17,0:18:35.84,Main01,Irie,0000,0000,0000,,Z-zničena...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.22,0:18:40.27,Main01,Irie,0000,0000,0000,,Neuvěřitelné...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.88,0:20:20.56,Main01,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.56,0:20:25.71,Main01,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,It's another episode of everyone's favorite "Haru's Haru-Haru Dangerous Interviews!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.71,0:20:27.60,Main01,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Today's guest is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.54,0:20:31.04,Main01,Ryohei,0000,0000,0000,,Ryohei Sasagawa! To the limit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.47,0:20:32.83,Main01,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Eek!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.83,0:20:34.33,Main01,Reborn,0000,0000,0000,,He's raring to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.33,0:20:36.27,Main01,Ryohei,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! To the limit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.27,0:20:41.02,Main01,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,That "to the limit" phrase hasn't changed from ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.02,0:20:42.98,Main01,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Do you still use it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.98,0:20:46.49,Main01,Ryohei,0000,0000,0000,,Lately, I've been more into Maximum Ingram.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.49,0:20:49.49,Main01,Reborn,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't "maximum" mean the same thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.49,0:20:51.82,Main01,Ryohei,0000,0000,0000,,Maximum Climax!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.19,0:20:54.13,Main01,Ryohei,0000,0000,0000,,Maximum Beeline!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.55,0:20:56.62,Main01,Ryohei,0000,0000,0000,,Maximum Unlimited!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.44,0:20:59.12,Main01,Ryohei,0000,0000,0000,,I considered all of those,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.12,0:21:02.87,Main01,Ryohei,0000,0000,0000,,but I felt that Maximum Ingram was more to the limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.87,0:21:05.78,Main01,Reborn,0000,0000,0000,,You can't get away from that phrase, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.18,0:21:07.16,Main01,Ryohei,0000,0000,0000,,To the limit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.16,0:21:08.33,Main01,Ryohei,0000,0000,0000,,That's how a man should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.81,0:21:10.11,Main01,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I know what you mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.11,0:21:12.88,Main01,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,When I was coming up with a title for this corner,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.88,0:21:18.80,Main02,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I spent a long time debating between "dangerous," "destroy," or just leaving it to chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.80,0:21:21.26,Main01,Ryohei,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I completely understand that feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.26,0:21:22.71,Main01,Ryohei,0000,0000,0000,,That's how a man should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.71,0:21:23.93,Main01,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Eek!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.93,0:21:25.72,Main01,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.72,0:21:28.18,Main01,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a blushing young maiden!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.18,0:21:30.38,Main01,Ryohei,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.38,0:21:31.15,Main01,Ryohei,0000,0000,0000,,My bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.15,0:21:32.98,Main01,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.31,0:21:35.43,Main01,Reborn,0000,0000,0000,,You've grown up, Ryohei.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.66,0:21:36.84,Main01,Ryohei,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.84,0:21:39.16,Main01,Ryohei,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't age ten years for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.16,0:21:40.04,Main01,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.04,0:21:41.60,Main01,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,You've really matured.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.60,0:21:46.05,Main01,Ryohei,0000,0000,0000,,I'm able to wait the whole three minutes for a cup of ramen to finish now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.05,0:21:47.82,Main01,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't used to be able to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.54,0:21:51.59,Main01,Ryohei,0000,0000,0000,,You only get a one minute break in boxing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.59,0:21:54.99,Main01,Ryohei,0000,0000,0000,,I waited thirty seconds after putting in the hot water and took the last thirty seconds to eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.38,0:21:59.18,Main01,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,That's taking instant to a whole new level!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.18,0:22:00.93,Main01,Reborn,0000,0000,0000,,He's matured.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.93,0:22:03.20,Main01,Reborn,0000,0000,0000,,He even bought a gift for I-Pin.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.80,0:22:04.98,Main01,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.98,0:22:08.62,Main01,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,He gave I-Pin a doll; an appropriate gift for a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.62,0:22:10.01,Main01,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,What did he give everyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.41,0:22:12.65,Main01,Ryohei,0000,0000,0000,,I gave octopus head octopus headphones!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.65,0:22:14.17,Main01,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Octopus headphones!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.17,0:22:15.03,Main01,Reborn,0000,0000,0000,,That's a no-brainer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.36,0:22:18.52,Main01,Ryohei,0000,0000,0000,,I gave Yamamoto a batting game with a disappearing pitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.52,0:22:19.86,Main01,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Disappearing pitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.86,0:22:20.77,Main01,Reborn,0000,0000,0000,,Another no-brainer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.15,0:22:25.01,Main01,Ryohei,0000,0000,0000,,And to encourage Sawada to aim for the sumo wrestling championship...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.43,0:22:28.33,Main01,Ryohei,0000,0000,0000,,I gave him an extreme Kesho-mawashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.43,0:22:32.93,On Screen,Ryohei,0000,0000,0000,,[Note: Ceremonial belt worn by Sumo wrestlers.]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.33,0:22:30.62,Main01,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Extreme Kesho-mawashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.90,0:22:32.93,Main01,Reborn,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.93,0:22:37.28,Main01,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuna-san looks so cool in that extreme Kesho-mawashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.28,0:22:38.45,Main01,Reborn,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.45,0:22:40.93,Main01,Ryohei,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to spend a night drinking with Hibari,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.93,0:22:43.88,Main01,Ryohei,0000,0000,0000,,so I bought some extremely good Italian wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.88,0:22:44.61,Main01,Hibari,0000,0000,0000,,No thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.61,0:22:46.96,Main01,Ryohei,0000,0000,0000,,But he turned me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.46,0:22:50.08,Main01,Reborn,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always up for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.08,0:22:51.03,Main01,Ryohei,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.03,0:22:51.76,Main01,Ryohei,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.76,0:22:53.15,Main01,Ryohei,0000,0000,0000,,Drink to the limit!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.15,0:22:54.26,Main01,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.26,0:22:57.50,Main01,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,A baby should not be drinking alcohol!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.50,0:22:58.78,Main01,Reborn,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be such a stiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.78,0:22:59.52,Main01,Ryohei,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.52,0:23:01.00,Main01,Ryohei,0000,0000,0000,,To the limit! To the limit!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.00,0:23:02.12,Main01,Ryohei,0000,0000,0000,,To the limit!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.12,0:23:04.74,Main01,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,That's all he ever says.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.74,0:23:07.28,Main01,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,You've been watching "Haru's Haru-Haru Dangerous Interviews!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.28,0:23:10.06,Main01,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Live from the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.06,0:23:14.16,Main01,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, we'll see you again next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.80,0:23:16.90,Main01,Tsuna,0000,0000,0000,,Next time:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.90,0:23:18.94,Main01,Tsuna,0000,0000,0000,,Resolve and Irritation.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.14,0:23:26.24,Main01,Tsuna,0000,0000,0000,,See you next time!!
